dc_title_s: Post's Addition to Ypsilanti; Surveyed and platted by C. S. Woodard.
dc_description_s: Shows Post's Addition subdivison to the City of Ypsilanti, Michigan. Official notarized record of the addition. Surveyed and platted January, 1875 by C. S. Woodard. 1 map: 44 x 49 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
